## âš™ï¸ Functions

| Function     | Description                          | Access      |
|--------------|--------------------------------------|-------------|
| `mint()`     | Owner-only minting                   | `onlyOwner` |
| `burn()`     | User can burn their own tokens       | External    |
| `pause()`    | Pause all token transfers            | `onlyOwner` |
| `unpause()`  | Resume token transfers               | `onlyOwner` |

